1.0.name: wordpress/nextgen-facebook
1.0.description:
An essential plugin for every WordPress website.

Open Graph and SEO

NGFB Open Graph+ adds Open Graph and (optionally) Search Engine Optimization (SEO) HTML tags to the head section of webpages. These HTML tags are used by Google Search and most social websites, to describe and display your content correctly (title, description, keyword tags, images, videos, author profile, etc.). See examples from Google Search, Facebook, Twitter (Cards), Pinterest, StumbleUpon, Tumblr, and others.

NGFB Open Graph+ is also excellent for extending and improving traditional SEO plugins like Yoast WordPress SEO, All-In-One SEO, SEO Ultimate, etc.

Find out more... What are Open Graph and Twitter Card Meta
